OL,3,CAutoimmune condition forces MP to self-
OL,4,Cisolate
OL,6,FChippenham's MP has to self-isolate
OL,7,Fwhile undergoing treatment for a newly
OL,8,Fdiagnosed autoimmune condition, her
OL,9,Foffice has revealed.
OL,11,FLiberal Democrat Sarah Gibson spent
OL,12,Ftwo weeks in intensive care at Bath's
OL,13,FRoyal United Hospital over Christmas
OL,14,Fand returned to Parliament in March.
OL,16,FNow, she says after being "closely
OL,17,Fmonitored" by NHS staff over the past
OL,18,Fsix months: "My recovery has proved
OL,19,Fslower than I anticipated."
