OL,6,FMs Gibson added: "Following a series
OL,7,Fof tests, my doctors have discovered
OL,8,Fthat I have developed an autoimmune
OL,9,Fcondition.
OL,11,F"The nature of this condition means I
OL,12,Fwill require a short period of
OL,13,Fmonitored treatment at the hospital."
OL,15,FThe MP will now have to self-isolate
OL,16,Ffor the duration of the treatment and
OL,17,Fwill continue her work virtually.
