OL,6,FShe added: "I continue to remain fully
OL,7,Fcommitted to working on your behalf,
OL,8,Falbeit virtually, and my office will
OL,9,Fremain fully operational during my
OL,10,Ftreatment.
OL,12,F"Once again, my thanks go to our local
OL,13,FNHS services, who are doing an
OL,14,Fincredible job under immense pressure."
