OL,7,Fconstituency from the Conservatives in
OL,8,Fthe General Election last July. She
OL,9,Ffell seriously in December following a
OL,10,Fparliamentary visit to Estonia to meet
OL,11,Ftroops. When she got back, she
OL,12,Fdeveloped pericarditis.
